1. *Pišem* knjigu. (I am writing a book.)
2. Uvek *pišem* kada imam vremena. (I always write when I have time.)
3. Ona *píše* priče za decu. (She writes stories for children.)
4. *Pisali* smo pisma jedno drugom. (We wrote letters to each other.)
5. *Pisah* ti puno stvari. (I wrote you a lot of things.)